NAME
  VTK::FiltersHybridRendering
LIBRARY_NAME
  vtkFiltersHybridRendering
DESCRIPTION
  The view/camera-dependent filters split out of FiltersHybrid: they require
  RenderingCore (vtkCamera/vtkRenderer/vtkRenderWindow). Kept in their own module
  so VTK::FiltersHybrid stays rendering-free.
